{"id":86937,"date":"2022-08-13T09:21:30","date_gmt":"2022-08-13T07:21:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=86937"},"modified":"2022-08-13T09:33:51","modified_gmt":"2022-08-13T07:33:51","slug":"albufeira","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/albufeira\/","title":{"rendered":"9 Best Things to do in Albufeira, Portugal"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">Things to do in Albufeira, Portugal<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Albufeira is one of the many whitewashed fisherman&#x2019;s villages on the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/algarve\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Algarve<\/a> coast. It&#x2019;s located on top of a low cliff and offers magnificent views over a grand beach and stunning waters, making it a popular tourist destination in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/europe\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Europe<\/a>. Most notably, it&#x2019;s where enthusiastic party and beach-goers like to spend their vacation. But there are many more things to do in Albufeira.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115948\/albufeira-portugal-4.jpg\" alt=\"things to do albufeira portugal colorful door\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do albufeira portugal colorful door\" class=\"wp-image-87159 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115948\/albufeira-portugal-4.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115948\/albufeira-portugal-4-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/