a-portugal-18-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120252\/albufeira-portugal-18-640x853.jpg 640w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120252\/albufeira-portugal-18-150x200.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120252\/albufeira-portugal-18-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120252\/albufeira-portugal-18.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-2-benagil-cave\">2. Benagil Cave<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Albufeira&#x2019;s rugged environment hosts some impressive natural wonders, including the otherworldly Benagil Cave. Located to the west of Albufeira, just off Benagil beach, you&#x2019;ll find an impressive cave with a worn circle in the ceiling, created by natural erosion. Through this distinctive hole, the blazing Portuguese sun casts its beams, shining a unique light into the cave.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5.jpg\" alt=\"Benagil Cave portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"296\" alt=\"Benagil Cave portugal\" class=\"wp-image-87161 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-800x526.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-1080x710.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-450x296.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-163x107.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-274x180.jpg 274w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-768x505.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-1024x674.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-1440x947.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-300x197.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-600x395.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-150x99.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120003\/albufeira-portugal-5.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>This natural highlight of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/algarve\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Algarve<\/a> can only be seen by boat, SUP, or kayak. Taking a boat trip to the Benagil Cave is a lot of fun and can be done from the Albufeira Marina. However, boats are unfortunately not allowed to enter the cave. This way, you won&#x2019;t be able to see the cave from the inside. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1.jpg\" alt=\"albufeira best beaches portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"albufeira best beaches portugal\" class=\"wp-image-87150 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-150x188.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115851\/albufeira-portugal-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Alternatively, you can make your own way there. If you travel to Benagil beach, you can rent a standup paddleboard or kayak and make your way to the cave from the beach. Visiting the Benagil Cave is one of the best things to do in Albufeira.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Please note:<\/strong> Although it&#x2019;s a short distance from Benagil beach to the cave, swimming is not advised due to the strong undertow and quickly changing tides.<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div data-vi-partner-id=\"P00037894\" data-vi-language=\"en\" data-vi-currency=\"USD\" data-vi-partner-type=\"AFFILIATE\" data-vi-url=\"163787P3,2236P6,28622P2\" data-vi-campaign=\"albufeira-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-viator\" data-script=\"https:\/\/www.viator.com\/orion\/partner\/widget.js\"><\/div>\n            \n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufeira-portugal-16.jpg\" alt=\"things to do albufeira marina\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do albufeira marina\" class=\"wp-image-87183 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufeira-portugal-16.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufeira-portugal-16-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufeira-portugal-16-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufeira-portugal-16-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufeira-portugal-16-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufeira-portugal-16-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufeira-portugal-16-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufeira-portugal-16-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufeira-portugal-16-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufeira-portugal-16-1440x1080.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufeira-portugal-16-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120223\/albufei