ontent\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-1080x719.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-1440x959.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-150x100.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121928\/albufeira-portugal-25.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The real highlight here, however, is the path along the cliffsides that give you some jaw-dropping views of the surroundings. Follow a 1.5-kilometer walk, passing the Arco Natural, a heart-shaped rock formation, towards the famous Benagil Cave. Getting to Marinha Beach from Albufeira is about a 30-minute ride by car and makes a perfect stop on your Portugal road trip. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/rent-car-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Read more about renting a car in Portugal.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-albufeira\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Albufeira.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121916\/albufeira-portugal-24.jpg\" alt=\"things to do albufeira Marinha Beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do albufeira Marinha Beach\" class=\"wp-image-87207 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121916\/albufeira-portugal-24.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08121