ourhair.com\/portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Portugal<\/a> town is still evident as you watch the fishing boats bring fresh seafood to the restaurants. You&#x2019;ll find some of the best restaurants and shops here!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/beautiful-villages-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The most beautiful villages in Portugal<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120356\/albufeira-portugal-22.jpg\" alt=\"things to do albufeira carvoeiro\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"things to do albufeira carvoeiro\" class=\"wp-image-87195 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120356\/albufeira-portugal-22.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120356\/albufeira-portugal-22-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120356\/albufeira-portugal-22-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120356\/albufeira-portugal-22-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120356\/albufeira-portugal-22-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-co