a> in the Algarve. It has maintained its traditional charm with its whitewashed houses, cobbled hillside streets full of flowers, and fishing boats on the river mouth. Like Carvoeiro, this is a picturesque town, so bring your camera! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115906\/albufeira-portugal-2.jpg\" alt=\"things to do albufeira day trip ferragudo\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do albufeira day trip ferragudo\" class=\"wp-image-87152 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115906\/albufeira-portugal-2.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115906\/albufeira-portugal-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115906\/albufeira-portugal-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115906\/albufeira-portugal-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115906\/albufeira-portugal-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115906\/albufeira-portugal-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115906\/albufeira-portugal-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115906\/albufeira-portugal-2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115906\/albufeira-portugal-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115906\/albufeira-portugal-2-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08115906\/albufeira-portugal-2-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/