3 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-800x538.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-1080x726.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-450x303.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-163x110.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-268x180.jpg 268w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-768x516.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-1024x689.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-1440x968.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-300x202.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-600x403.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-150x101.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120015\/albufeira-portugal-6.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>About an hour&#x2019;s drive from Albufeira lies Praia do Amado (Amado Beach), which is an excellent place to practice your surfing skills. The rolling hills and cliffs behind the sweeping bay cause high winds, making it a popular spot for international surf competitions and lessons. Spend the day here catching a few waves and stay to watch the sunset.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-albufeira\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Albufeira.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120211\/albufeira-portugal-15.jpg\" alt=\"things to do albufeira portugal boat tour\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do albufeira portugal boat tour\" class=\"wp-image-87181 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120211\/albufeira-portugal-15.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120211\/albufeira-portugal-15-800x600.jpg 800w,