nner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-7-albufeira-old-town\">7. Albufeira Old Town<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Apart from exploring the surroundings, spend some time in the old town of Albufeira. You&#x2019;ll find cute cobblestone streets, whitewashed and tiled houses, a few museums, picturesque churches, and plenty of restaurants, stores, and bars. Walk around the heart of the village for an hour, stopping at beautiful viewpoints overlooking the beach.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120132\/albufeira-portugal-12.jpg\" alt=\"albufeira things to do portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"albufeira things to do portugal\" class=\"wp-image-87175 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120132\/albufeira-portugal-12.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120132\/albufeira-portugal-12-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120132\/albufeira-portugal-12-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120132\/albufeira-portugal-12-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120132\/albufeira-portugal-12-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120132\/albufeira-portugal-12-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120132\/albufeira-portugal-12-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120132\/albufeira-portugal-12-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120132\/albufeira-portugal-12-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-con