                  <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-camping-in-albufeira\">Camping in Albufeira<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you discovering Portugal on a road trip in a campervan? Albufeira makes a fun stopover and offers a few campsites not too far outside of town.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/travel-portugal-campervan\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How to travel Portugal by Campervan<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"transport\">How to Visit Albufeira&#xA0;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Albufeira is the largest resort town of the Algarve, making it a popular tourist destination. You can fly to the main international airport of southern Portugal: Faro Airport, about 36 KM (22.4 miles) east of Albufeira.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--flight \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--flight\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/flights-faro\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your flight to Faro, Portugal<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9.jpg\" alt=\"where to stay albufeira portugal\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"where to stay albufeira portugal\" class=\"wp-image-87169 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/08120052\/albufeira-portugal-9-150x22